query:
UPDATE transactions
            SET
                in_mempool = FALSE
            FROM (
                SELECT
                    UNNEST($1::bytea []) AS address,
                    UNNEST($2::numeric []) AS nonce_key
            ) AS s
            WHERE
                transactions.in_mempool = TRUE
                AND transactions.initiator_address = s.address
                AND transactions.nonce_key = s.nonce_key
